snippet: Top-ranked Baylor got a career-high 41 points from Brittney Griner as it completed its first undefeated season in a 77-53 win against Iowa State.
abstract: College Basketball Women's Roundup; Baylor defeats Iowa State, 77-53, behind center Britney Griner's career-high 41 points; other women's college scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Baylor got a career-high 41 points from Brittney Griner as it completed its first undefeated season in a 77-53 win against Iowa State.

headline.seo: Griner Scores 41 as No. 1 Baylor Blasts Iowa State
headline.main: Baylor Stays Unbeaten as Griner Scores 41
